{"parents": [], "prev": null, "next": null, "title": "Ask Question Block", "meta": {}, "body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"ask-question-block\">\n<h1>Ask Question Block<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#ask-question-block\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h1>\n<div class=\"line-block\">\n<div class=\"line\">The <strong>Ask Question</strong> block is only available when designing a workflow for a <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/campaigns/guides/voice/voice_campaigns.html\">voice campaign</a> or when managing a workflow for a <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/phone/guides/numbers/phone_numbers.html\">phone number</a> .</div>\n</div>\n<ol class=\"arabic simple\">\n<li><p>Place a <strong>Ask Question</strong> block in your workflow where desired</p></li>\n<li><p>Enter a question</p></li>\n<li><p>Click <strong>Done</strong></p></li>\n<li><p>Click <strong>Add Answer</strong></p></li>\n<li><p>Select <strong>equals</strong>, <strong>does not equal</strong>, <strong>contains</strong>, or <strong>does not contain</strong> (click <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/general/guides/functions_of_the_grid/criteria_options.html\">here</a> for definitions)</p></li>\n<li><p>Enter a word or phrase</p></li>\n<li><p>Click <strong>Add</strong></p></li>\n<li><p>To add another answer, click <strong>Add Answer</strong> again</p></li>\n<li><p>To delete an answer, click <i class=\"fa fa-times\"></i></p></li>\n<li><p>To edit &lt;/users/general/guides/functions_of_the_grid/how_to_edit.html&gt;`_ an answer, click <i class=\"fa fa-pencil\"></i></p></li>\n<li><p>Click <strong>Done</strong></p></li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n", "metatags": "", "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"]], "sourcename": "users/automation/guides/workflows/ask_question_block.rst.txt", "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">Ask Question Block</a></li>\n</ul>\n", "display_toc": false, "page_source_suffix": ".rst", "current_page_name": "users/automation/guides/workflows/ask_question_block", "sidebars": ["localtoc.html", "relations.html", "sourcelink.html", "searchbox.html"], "customsidebar": null, "favicon_url": null, "logo_url": null, "alabaster_version": "0.7.12"}